pen... #OOTT", "time": "01:13", "author": "Cheekybaua", "author_name": "Mista Indigo", "followers": 1570, "views": 6015, "likes": 114, "replies": 15, "retweets": 12, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069626575524421959", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2069626575524421959", "text": "Petronas makes new gas find at Suriname offshore block, discoveries equivalent to 1 billion barrels #oott https://t.co/Ht7nmMdyXN", "time": "03:40", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 4726, "likes": 7, "replies": 0, "retweets": 4, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069640590732476423", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2069640590732476423", "text": "Trump post on gasoline #oott https://t.co/ysPUPBA5kc", "time": "04:35", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 14723, "likes": 72, "replies": 25, "retweets": 14, "quotes": 7, "bookmarks": 18, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069641570475782486", "url": "https://x.com/NuggetCapital/status/2069641570475782486", "text": "Trump is back to terrorize the oil bulls.\n\nBetcha Texas oilmen want their votes back. #OOTT", "time": "04:39", "author": "NuggetCapital", "author_name": "Nugget Capital Partners (NCP)", "followers": 7677, "views": 9821, "likes": 72, "replies": 13, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069666609455677563", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2069666609455677563", "text": "A supertanker has been provisionally booked to transport oil from the Persian Gulf to India at a rate equivalent to almost nine times benchmark freight costs, an eye-watering price that reflects the shortage of available, empty vessels in the area.\n#oott https://t.co/3T5fS31Y7U", "time": "06:19", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 18841, "likes": 156, "replies": 2, "retweets": 49, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 21, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069700017263378875", "url": "https://x.com/JuneGoh_Sparta/status/2069700017263378875", "text": "It was a pleasure being on @gulf_intel today, representing @SpartaCommo. Here are my thoughts (yes, I did promise a deeper discussion after my lovely vacation in Beijing-Tianjin).\n\nAsia moves from drought to flood, at least for a while until China starts to buy again.\n\n#oott https://t.co/h4Hs2WqJ1e", "time": "08:31", "author": "JuneGoh_Sparta", "author_name": "June Goh", "followers": 18022, "views": 7391, "likes": 34, "replies": 3, "retweets": 6, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 14, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069722988488863908", "url": "https://x.com/NuggetCapital/status/2069722988488863908", "text": "Does @HFI_Research do refunds??? lol 🤣\n\n\"Refineries in the East have already ​been well supplied for the next two months and have no need for the incremental barrels, leading to a very weak market and Dubai spreads in contango,\" said ​June Goh \n\n#OOTT", "time": "10:03", "author": "NuggetCapital", "author_name": "Nugget Capital Partners (NCP)", "followers": 7677, "views": 18840, "likes": 58, "replies": 6, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 12, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069730000270409965", "url": "https://x.com/garquake/status/2069730000270409965", "text": "Historical and future strip commodity prices\nCrude oil - WTI\nCrude oil - Brent\nNatural gas - Henry Hub\n\nLots on negative pressure of late as oil gushing back ino market with Iran / Strait of Hormuz flowing #oott https://t.co/1p7yPS41qX", "time": "10:31", "author": "garquake", "author_name": "Burnsco", "followers": 32104, "views": 3056, "likes": 11, "replies": 4, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069734111678247253", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2069734111678247253", "text": "Reuters says oil markets are suddenly oversupplied.\n\nBut production hasn’t surged. Demand hasn’t collapsed.\n\nWhat’s changed is that trapped barrels are moving again and the Hormuz fear premium has evaporated.\n\nThat’s not a glut. It’s a traffic jam clearing. #Oil #OOTT #EnergyMarkets #Hormuz \n\nhttps:", "time": "10:47", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 29236, "likes": 351, "replies": 43, "retweets": 45, "quotes": 8, "bookmarks": 36, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069745816273608753", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2069745816273608753", "text": "Moscow oil refinery hit by drone attacks is unlikely to resume production this year, sources say #oott https://t.co/5i4Q2GL8jw", "time": "11:33", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 7319, "likes": 11, "replies": 1, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069767914597879837", "url": "https://x.com/DarioCpx/status/2069767914597879837", "text": "JustDarioDaily - Podcast\n\n⚠️ Hormuz Crisis Watch: Brent Crude Shorts at Extreme Levels 🎙️ \n\n#OOTT\n\nhttps://t.co/1Cf6GtJdQG", "time": "13:01", "author": "DarioCpx", "author_name": "JustDario", "followers": 113106, "views": 121413, "likes": 150, "replies": 27, "retweets": 17, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 21, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069789247603962024", "url": "https://x.com/LVision_Trading/status/2069789247603962024", "text": "IMO: hundreds of vessels can now leave the Persian Gulf via Hormuz\n\nMarkets: oil bath. $73.5\n\nMe: count the ducklings. 89 crude tankers. ~135M bbls max - indulge in every pleasure.\n\nExits outpacing entries today.\n\nWhen the last duckling leaves what happens?\n\n$OIL #OOTT NFA", "time": "14:26", "author": "LVision_Trading", "author_name": "Laman", "followers": 1924, "views": 16767, "likes": 146, "replies": 18, "retweets": 13, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 16, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069790427410993305", "url": "https://x.com/JuliOnTwtr/status/2069790427410993305", "text": "EIA WPSR Inventory moves\n\nCrude -6.1 million \nGasoline +2.1 million \nDistillates +3.1 million \n\n#oott #crudeoil #eiawpsr", "time": "14:31", "author": "JuliOnTwtr", "author_name": "Julianne Geiger", "followers": 8674, "views": 12022, "likes": 140, "replies": 9, "retweets": 16, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069790534613315606", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2069790534613315606", "text": "#OOTT | US DoE Crude Oil Inventories (W/W) 19-Jun: -6.088M (est -3.60M; prev -8.263M)\n- Distillate: +3.064M (est -1.05M; prev +951K)\n- Cushing: -1.077M (prev -1.606M)\n- Gasoline: +2.064M (est -1.097M; prev -906K)\n- Refinery: -0.60% (est -0.34% prev 1.40%)", "time": "14:31", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 436347, "views": 13965, "likes": 6, "replies": 0, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069791394479149067", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2069791394479149067", "text": "US crude inventories fell by 15.148mb\n(commercial: -6.088mb, SPR -9.060mb)\nEIA #oott", "time": "14:34", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 10317, "likes": 101, "replies": 7, "retweets": 10, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069804439482114250", "url": "https://x.com/avionsunantiqu1/status/2069804439482114250", "text": "Iran\n\nGet all loaded tankers out ✅\n\nGet Frozen money return guaranteed by Qatar &amp; SA ✅\n\nDon't budge on Israel to leave Lebanon ✅\n\nSlow or close Hormuz\n\nLet Western oil inventories continue to decline\n\nLet oil prices rise, and strangle US economy until Trump gets the boot.#OOTT", "time": "15:26", "author": "avionsunantiqu1", "author_name": "Nicholas James", "followers": 1433, "views": 6333, "likes": 117, "replies": 13, "retweets": 16, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 9, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069806840695967988", "url": "https://x.com/a4_alpha/status/2069806840695967988", "text": "TMF, the numbers do not lie. China may not be a buyer today but demand is not falling and inventories are drawing. I expect a united front to talk #energy prices lower as it is a risk to the global economy. This is an opportunity for those who see it.\n\nThank you #OOTT #EFT #COM", "time": "15:36", "author": "a4_alpha", "author_name": "A4Alpha", "followers": 7996, "views": 84268, "likes": 317, "replies": 5, "retweets": 9, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 77, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069811106177229025", "url": "https://x.com/TankerTrackers/status/2069811106177229025", "text": "Iran has exported 40 million barrels of crude oil since 2026-06-15. Exactly half of that amount shipped out in a single day; which was last Friday (2026-06-19).\n\n#OOTT #IranWar #Tankers", "time": "15:53", "author": "TankerTrackers", "author_name": "TankerTrackers.com, Inc.", "followers": 227035, "views": 168737, "likes": 402, "replies": 14, "retweets": 96, "quotes": 33, "bookmarks": 45, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069924720632295749", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2069924720632295749", "text": "One week ago Hormuz was the world's biggest energy crisis in history\n\nToday analysts are talking about an oil glut\n\nNothing material has changed—only the narrative\n\nMarkets can reprice fear overnight\n\nGeopolitics doesn't\n\n#Oil #OOTT #Hormuz #Energy #Geopolitics\n\nhttps://t.co/jArVZij2O4", "time": "23:24", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 5885, "likes": 137, "replies": 7, "retweets": 16, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069925230655471731", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2069925230655471731", "text": "Oil prices are back near pre-war levels\n\nBut inventories keep falling toward record lows\n\nEveryone is watching barrels leaving Hormuz\n\nFar fewer are watching the barrels going back in\n\nThe IRGC can count barrels too\n\n#OOTT #Oil #Hormuz #Energy #Geopolitics", "time": "23:26", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 14629, "likes": 192, "replies": 10, "retweets": 28, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 14, "labels": n